  81,22,"wma muhamad aldhy terfwnh bmjnwn, walaqad ra'aa muhamad jbryl aldhy yatih balrsalt fi al'ufuq alezym, wama hu bbkhyl fi tblygh alwhy. wama hdha alquran biqawl shaytan rjym, mtrwd min rahmat allh, wlknh kalam allah wwhyh"
  81,23,"wma muhamad aldhy terfwnh bmjnwn, walaqad ra'aa muhamad jbryl aldhy yatih balrsalt fi al'ufuq alezym, wama hu bbkhyl fi tblygh alwhy. wama hdha alquran biqawl shaytan rjym, mtrwd min rahmat allh, wlknh kalam allah wwhyh"
